{"id":721422782,"lang":"python3","lang_name":"Python3","time":"1 year, 3 months","timestamp":1655142777,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"140 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/721422782/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"14.1 MB","code":"class Solution:\n    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s: str) -> int:\n        start, end = 0, 0\n        hashmap = {}\n        maxlen = 0\n        while end < len(s):\n            # check whether end in hashmap\n            # if not, add s[end++] and update max_len\n            if s[end] not in hashmap.keys() or hashmap[s[end]] == 0:\n                hashmap[s[end]] = 1\n                end += 1\n                maxlen = max(maxlen, end - start)\n            # else, increment start and update hashmap until hashmap[s[end]] is 0\n            else:\n                while hashmap[s[end]] > 0:\n                    hashmap[s[start]] -= 1\n                    start += 1\n        return maxlen","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
